---
import GifFooter from './GifFooter.astro';
---

<footer id="about">

  <!-- Footer columns -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8" style="padding: 88px 20px 8px; line-height: 0.65;">

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-geist text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">About</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 max-w-sm">
        <div class="lang-en space-y-3">
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">My name is Manu Bedacarratz, you can also call me Manol.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">I work as a designer and animator from Buenos Aires for Argentina and the world. My work spans brand identities and motion systems to posters, album covers and music videos.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">I'm especially drawn to design that leaves the screen. Projects that end up printed, pasted on a wall, pressed on vinyl. There's something about that physicality that feels important, especially now. What I enjoy most about this job is doing it with others: friends, colleagues, musicians, artists.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">If you're working on something and think we could make something good together, reach out.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lang-es space-y-3">
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">Mi nombre es Manu Bedacarratz, también me dicen Manol.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">Trabajo como diseñador y animador desde Buenos Aires para Argentina y el mundo. Mi trabajo abarca desde identidades de marca y sistemas animados hasta posters, tapas de discos y videoclips.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">Me interesa especialmente el diseño que sale de la pantalla. Proyectos que terminan impresos, que se pegan en una pared, que se graban en vinilo. Hay algo en esa materialidad que me parece importante, especialmente hoy. Lo que más disfruto de mi oficio es hacerlo con otros: amigos, colegas, músicos, artistas.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">Si estás trabajando en algo y creés que podemos hacer algo bueno juntos, escribime.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="lang-en">
        <h2 class="font-geist text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">Services</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {['Brand identities', 'Motion & animated systems', 'Album covers and visual art', 'Posters and graphic pieces', 'Music videos and audiovisual work'].map(s => (
            <li class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">{s}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="lang-es">
        <h2 class="font-geist text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">Servicios</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {['Identidades de marca', 'Motion & sistemas animados', 'Tapas de discos y arte visual', 'Posters y piezas gráficas', 'Videoclips y piezas audiovisuales'].map(s => (
            <li class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">{s}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-geist text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">Partners &amp; colleagues</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        {[
          { name: 'Paisanos',  url: 'https://www.paisanos.io/es' },

          { name: 'Paradigma', url: 'https://paradigma.cc/' },
          { name: 'Aerolab',   url: 'https://aerolab.co/' },
          { name: 'Almanach',  url: 'https://almanach.work/' },
          { name: 'Joyco',     url: 'https://joyco.studio/' },
        ].map(p => (
          <li>
            <a
              href={p.url}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors"
            >
              {p.name}
            </a>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="lang-en">
        <h2 class="font-geist text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-3">If you think we could collaborate, drop me a message here.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lang-es">
        <h2 class="font-geist text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">Contacto</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-3">Si creés que podemos colaborar, dejame un mensaje acá.</p>
      </div>
      <a
        href="mailto:manubedacarratz@gmail.com"
        class="block mt-2 text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors"
      >
        manubedacarratz@gmail.com
      </a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-4" style="margin-top: 16px;">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/___manol___/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors">
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/>
            <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="0.8" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://vimeo.com/manuellbedacarratz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors">
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M22 7.42c-.09 2.09-1.55 4.95-4.39 8.58C14.68 19.8 12.2 21.6 10.12 21.6c-1.29 0-2.38-1.19-3.26-3.57L5.3 12.18C4.6 9.8 3.83 8.6 3.02 8.6c-.18 0-.8.38-1.86 1.13L0 8.32c1.17-1.03 2.33-2.06 3.47-3.09C5.1 3.8 6.32 3.11 7.15 3.04c2.02-.19 3.26 1.19 3.73 4.13.5 3.17.85 5.14 1.06 5.92.59 2.67 1.23 4 1.93 4 .54 0 1.37-.86 2.47-2.58 1.1-1.72 1.69-3.03 1.77-3.93.16-1.48-.43-2.22-1.77-2.22-.63 0-1.28.14-1.95.44 1.3-4.24 3.77-6.3 7.43-6.17C23.97 2.7 22.13 4.83 22 7.42z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/manuel-bedacarratz/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors">
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/>
            <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/>
            <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: -70px;">
    <GifFooter marginBottom="-90px" />
  </div>

</footer>
